Design



animal population simulator

user inputs number of predators, prey and time frame, then the program simulates the fluctions in the population over time 
and then outputs the changes in the population and the final population.


Classes:

animal
eat
breed
age


predator
hunt (polymorphism of eat)


prey



main function

call function that creates the animals using user input to determine number of predators and number of prey and time frame.





